</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="19.[809,1426,346,1411]" pageId="19">
For a description and a justification to consider this name a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Charpentier" baseAuthorityYear="1837" box="[1113,1231,1358,1380]" class="Gastropoda" family="Pupillidae" genus="Pupilla" kingdom="Animalia" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="19" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="alpicola">
<emphasis box="[1113,1231,1358,1380]" italics="true" pageId="19">P. alpicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
see the 
<emphasis box="[1326,1425,1358,1379]" italics="true" pageId="19">Material</emphasis>
section and our present comparisons.
</paragraph>
